        "custom_liquid": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n<title>PuppyPad™ 4 in 1 Reusable Training Pad</title>\n<style>\n  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n\n  :root {\n    --black: #111827;\n    --white: #ffffff;\n    --gray-light: #f5f6f7;\n    --gray-mid: #e0e0e0;\n    --gray-text: #666;\n    --accent: #2f6fed;\n    --accent-dark: #1f4fb0;\n    --green: #1a7f5a;\n    --gold: #f4a261;\n    --font: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  body { font-family: var(--font); color: var(--black); background: var(--white); line-height: 1.6; }\n\n  /* ── CUSTOMER BANNER ── */\n  .customer-banner {\n    background: var(--black);\n    color: var(--white);\n    padding: 14px 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  .customer-banner span { color: var(--gold); }\n\n  /* ── SECTION TITLES ── */\n  .section-title {\n    font-size: 30px; font-weight: 800; text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;\n  }\n  .section-subtitle {\n    text-align: center; color: var(--gray-text); font-size: 16px;\n    margin-bottom: 50px; max-width: 680px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\n  }\n\n  /* ── FEEL BETTER ── */\n  .feel-section { padding: 80px 5%; background: var(--white); }\n  .feel-inner {\n    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center;\n  }\n  .feel-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: 14px; object-fit: cover; height: 520px; }\n  .feel-text h2 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.2; }\n  .feel-text p { font-size: 16px; color: #444; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.7; }\n  .feel-text ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }\n  .feel-text ul li {\n    padding: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-mid);\n    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .feel-text ul li::before {\n    content: \"✓\"; color: var(--green); font-weight: 900; font-size: 17px;\n    flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── TESTIMONIAL QUOTE ── */\n  .quote-box {\n    background: var(--gray-light); border-left: 5px solid var(--accent);\n    padding: 24px 28px; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; margin-top: 32px;\n  }\n  .quote-box p { font-style: italic; font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin-bottom: 12px; }\n  .quote-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }\n  .avatar { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; }\n  .author-info strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }\n  .author-info span { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-text); }\n  .stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; }\n\n  /* ── HOW IT WORKS (dark) ── */\n  .how-section { background: var(--black); padding: 80px 5%; color: var(--white); }\n  .how-section .section-title { color: var(--white); }\n  .how-section .section-subtitle { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }\n  .how-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 28px; }\n  .how-card {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);\n    border-radius: 14px; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center;\n  }\n  .how-card .icon-wrap {\n    width: 64px; height: 64px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n    margin: 0 auto 20px; font-size: 28px;\n  }\n  .how-card h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--white); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }\n  .how-card p { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height: 1.6; }\n\n  /* ── PUPPYPAD vs DISPOSABLES ── */\n  .upgrade-section { background: var(--gray-light); padding: 80px 5%; }\n  .upgrade-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; margin-top: 40px; }\n  .upgrade-card { background: var(--white); border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; border: 2px solid var(--gray-mid); }\n  .upgrade-card.winner { border-color: var(--black); }\n  .upgrade-card-header { padding: 18px 24px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background: var(--gray-mid); color: var(--black); }\n  .upgrade-card.winner .upgrade-card-header { background: var(--black); color: var(--white); }\n  .upgrade-card img { width: 100%; height: 220px; object-fit: contain; padding: 16px; background: #fafafa; display: block; }\n  .upgrade-list { list-style: none; padding: 20px 24px; }\n  .upgrade-list li { padding: 9px 0; font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }\n  .upgrade-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .check-green { color: var(--green); font-weight: 900; font-size: 16px; }\n  .check-red   { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 900; font-size: 16px; }\n\n  /* ── RESULTS ── */\n  .results-section { padding: 80px 5%; background: var(--white); }\n  .results-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }\n  .results-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: 14px; height: 500px; object-fit: cover; }\n  .stats-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; }\n  .stat-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; }\n  .stat-number { font-size: 52px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 90px; }\n  .stat-desc { font-size: 15px; color: #444; padding-top: 10px; line-height: 1.5; }\n  .stat-note { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-text); margin-top: 24px; font-style: italic; }\n\n  /* ── EXPERT TRUST ── */\n  .expert-section { background: var(--gray-light); padding: 80px 5%; text-align: center; }\n  .expert-img { border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; }\n  .expert-img img { width: 100%; display: block; }\n\n  /* ── GUARANTEE ── */\n  .guarantee-section { background: var(--black); color: var(--white); padding: 80px 5%; text-align: center; }\n  .guarantee-section h2 { font-size: 30px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 16px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }\n  .guarantee-section > p { font-size: 17px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto 48px; line-height: 1.7; }\n  .trust-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 20px; }\n  .trust-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 16px; }\n  .trust-card .trust-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }\n  .trust-card h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.3px; }\n  .trust-card p { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin: 0; }\n\n  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */\n  @media (max-width: 900px) {\n    .feel-inner, .results-inner, .upgrade-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .feel-img img, .results-img img { height: 320px; }\n    .how-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .trust-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }\n    .section-title { font-size: 24px; }\n    .stat-number { font-size: 40px; }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .feel-section, .how-section, .upgrade-section,\n    .results-section, .expert-section, .guarantee-section { padding: 50px 4%; }\n    .trust-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }\n    .trust-card { padding: 18px 12px; }\n    .trust-card .trust-icon { font-size: 26px; }\n    .trust-card h4 { font-size: 12px; }\n    .trust-card p { font-size: 11px; }\n    .guarantee-section h2 { font-size: 22px; }\n    .guarantee-section > p { font-size: 15px; }\n    .feel-text h2 { font-size: 24px; }\n    .stat-number { font-size: 36px; min-width: 72px; }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<!-- ── BANNER ── -->\n<div class=\"customer-banner\">🐾 Over <span>150,000+</span> Dog Parents — Zero Accidents Guaranteed</div>\n\n<!-- ── FEEL BETTER AGAIN ── -->\n<section class=\"feel-section\">\n  <div class=\"feel-inner\">\n    <div class=\"feel-img\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0433/0510/7612/files/the-solution.webp?v=1754686586\" alt=\"PuppyPad in use\" />\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"feel-text\">\n      <h2>Stop Cleaning Up Accidents for Good</h2>\n      <p>Whether it's a new puppy, a senior dog with an aging bladder, or a dog who's never quite gotten the hang of pads — accidents shouldn't run your household. PuppyPad targets the actual reason disposables fail with patented scent technology, right on your floor.</p>\n      <p>Using <strong>dog-attracting pheromone infusion</strong>, a 4-layer leak-proof core, and a chew-proof anti-slip shell, it gives your dog an unmistakable bathroom spot — recognized instantly, used consistently.</p>\n      <ul>\n        <li><div><strong>Ends accidents fast</strong> — Pheromone technology signals \"this is the spot\" the moment your dog sniffs it, no training required.</div></li>\n        <li><div><strong>Keeps floors bone dry</strong> — 4-layer absorption locks liquid away instantly, so nothing ever leaks through to your carpet or hardwood.</div></li>\n        <li><div><strong>Survives determined chewers</strong> — Military-grade fabric resists tearing, shredding, and digging, unlike flimsy disposables.</div></li>\n        <li><div><strong>Stays fresh, not funky</strong> — Antimicrobial core eliminates odor at the source instead of masking it between washes.</div></li>\n        <li><div><strong>Reusable 300+ times</strong> — Machine washable and built to last over a year, replacing a stack of disposables one pad at a time.</div></li>\n      </ul>\n      <div class=\"quote-box\">\n        <p>\"I put it down and my dachshund walked right over and used it like she'd known it her whole life. No training, no accidents since. I genuinely didn't believe it would work.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"quote-author\">\n          <img class=\"avatar\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0433/0510/7612/files/navyblue-checkmark.svg?v=1754231042\" alt=\"Linda M.\" />\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <strong>Linda M.</strong>\n            <span>Verified buyer</span>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ── -->\n<section class=\"how-section\">\n  <p class=\"section-title\">How PuppyPad Works</p>\n  <p class=\"section-subtitle\">Three engineered layers working together so your dog uses it — and your floors stay clean.</p>\n  <div class=\"how-grid\">\n    <div class=\"how-card\">\n      <div class=\"icon-wrap\">🐾</div>\n      <h3>Pheromone Technology</h3>\n      <p>Patented pheromones mimic the natural scent signals dogs use to mark territory — undetectable to you, irresistible to your dog's 300 million scent receptors.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"how-card\">\n      <div class=\"icon-wrap\">💧</div>\n      <h3>4-Layer Leak Protection</h3>\n      <p>A super-absorbent core traps liquid instantly and holds up to 10x more than disposable pads, keeping every drop off your floors, ever.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"how-card\">\n      <div class=\"icon-wrap\">🛡️</div>\n      <h3>Chew-Proof Shell</h3>\n      <p>Military-grade, tear-resistant fabric on an anti-slip base means it stays intact and stays put, even with the most determined chewers and diggers.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ── PUPPYPAD vs DISPOSABLES ── -->\n<section class=\"upgrade-section\">\n  <p class=\"section-title\">Why Switch From Disposables?</p>\n  <p class=\"section-subtitle\">We took everything disposable pads get wrong — and built a pad that actually works.</p>\n  <div class=\"upgrade-grid\">\n    <div class=\"upgrade-card winner\">\n      <div class=\"upgrade-card-header\">✅ PuppyPad — Reusable</div>\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0433/0510/7612/files/Gray-6Pads.png?v=1754244461\" alt=\"PuppyPad\" />\n      <ul class=\"upgrade-list\">\n        <li><span class=\"check-green\">✓</span> Pheromone technology, built-in</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-green\">✓</span> Chew-proof, tear-proof fabric</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-green\">✓</span> 4-layer, 100% leak-proof core</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-green\">✓</span> No smell — antimicrobial technology</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-green\">✓</span> $0 to replace after purchase</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-green\">✓</span> 90-day risk-free guarantee</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"upgrade-card\">\n      <div class=\"upgrade-card-header\">❌ Disposable Pee Pads</div>\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0433/0510/7612/files/the-problem.webp?v=1754686586\" alt=\"Disposable pads\" style=\"filter:grayscale(0.4);\" />\n      <ul class=\"upgrade-list\">\n        <li><span class=\"check-red\">✗</span> No scent technology</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-red\">✗</span> Destroyed in seconds</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-red\">✗</span> Leaks through to floor</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-red\">✗</span> Smell lingers between changes</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-red\">✗</span> $80–$100 forever, every month</li>\n        <li><span class=\"check-red\">✗</span> Single use, straight to landfill</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ── RESULTS ── -->\n<section class=\"results-section\">\n  <div class=\"results-inner\">\n    <div class=\"results-img\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0433/0510/7612/files/Pad-Size-Comparison.webp?v=1754523799\" alt=\"PuppyPad results\" />\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <h2 style=\"font-size:30px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:36px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;\">Fewer Accidents in Days, Not Weeks</h2>\n      <div class=\"stats-list\">\n        <div class=\"stat-item\">\n          <div class=\"stat-number\">99.5%</div>\n          <p class=\"stat-desc\">Of the 150,000+ orders placed were kept — fewer than 0.5% have ever been returned under our 90-day guarantee.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"stat-item\">\n          <div class=\"stat-number\">10x</div>\n          <p class=\"stat-desc\">More absorbent than a standard disposable pad, thanks to the 4-layer leak-proof core underneath every PuppyPad.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"stat-item\">\n          <div class=\"stat-number\">300+</div>\n          <p class=\"stat-desc\">Machine washes per pad, meaning one PuppyPad can realistically replace over a thousand single-use disposables.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"stat-note\">*Based on internal order and return data. Individual results may vary by dog.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ── VET RECOMMENDED ── -->\n<section class=\"expert-section\">\n  <p class=\"section-title\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">Vet Recommended</p>\n  <p class=\"section-subtitle\">Trusted by thousands of dog parents, groomers, and veterinary staff for house training, senior dogs, and multi-dog households.</p>\n  <div class=\"expert-img\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0433/0510/7612/files/StarRating.svg?v=1754231046\" alt=\"Vet recommended\" />\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ── GUARANTEE ── -->\n<section class=\"guarantee-section\">\n  <h2>Built to Last. Backed by a Real Guarantee.</h2>\n  <p>At PuppyPad, we believe every dog can learn where to go — and every home deserves to stay clean. Every pad is chew-tested, vet-recommended, and built to outlast a year of disposables. Try it risk-free with our 90-day guarantee — no questions asked.</p>\n  <div class=\"trust-grid\">\n    <div class=\"trust-card\">\n      <div class=\"trust-icon\">🛡️</div>\n      <h4>90-Day Guarantee</h4>\n      <p>Full refund if your dog doesn't take to it — no hoops, no hassle.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"trust-card\">\n      <div class=\"trust-icon\">🐾</div>\n      <h4>Pheromone Tested</h4>\n      <p>Patented scent technology developed to work across breeds, sizes, and ages.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"trust-card\">\n      <div class=\"trust-icon\">💬</div>\n      <h4>24/7 Support</h4>\n      <p>Our team responds within 24 hours, every day of the week.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"trust-card\">\n      <div class=\"trust-icon\">🌎</div>\n      <h4>Better for the Planet</h4>\n      <p>One reusable pad replaces a thousand disposables headed for landfill.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
